DAILY POST brings you the results of all the 2022 UEFA Nations League matches that took place on Wednesday. Belgium defeated Poland 6-1 at the King Baudouin Stadium. Goals from Axel Witsel, Kevin De Bruyne, Leandro Trossard (2), Leander Dendoncker and Lois Openda ensured Belgium defeated Poland. Robert Lewandowski did score the only goal for Poland against the host. Below are the results of the games played on Wednesday: A4 Belgium 6-1 Poland
A4 Wales 1-2 Netherlands
B1 Republic of Ireland 0-1 Ukraine
B1 Scotland 2-0 Armenia Meanwhile, matches continue today, Thursday 9 June: A2 Portugal vs Czech Republic
A2 Switzerland vs Spain
B4 Norway vs Slovenia
B4 Sweden vs Serbia
C2 Greece vs Cyprus
